%20by%20that%20model's%20ability%20to%20combat%20reflections.%20Most%20TVs%20have%20glossy%20screens%20that%20create%20a%20mirror-like%20effect%20in%20rooms%20with%20lots%20of%20light%20and%20windows.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20headache%20when%20you%20watch%20TV%20during%20the%20day.%20But%20the%20S95D's%20matte%20screen%20was%20a%20game%20changer%20and%20greatly%20reduced%20this%20problem.%20However%2C%20its%20anti-reflective%20panel%20caused%20dark%20scenes%20to%20look%20a%20bit%20washed%20out%20and%20hazy%20in%20a%20bright%20room.%20I'm%20hoping%20the%20S95F's%20improved%20glare-free%20tech%20fixes%20that%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20is%20also%20touting%20a%20brighter%20screen%20on%20the%20S95F%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20big%20statement%20since%20the%202024%20S95D%20is%20still%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20there%20is.%20Measurements%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20until%20hands-on%20testing%20later%20this%20year%2C%20but%20based%20on%20rumblings%20about%20the%20S95F's%20new%20QD-OLED%20panel%2C%20I'm%20expecting%20it%20to%20hit%20at%20least%202%2C000%20nits.%20That%20would%20be%20an%20impressive%20feat%20for%20an%20OLED%20and%20would%20make%20this%20an%20excellent%20set%20for%20people%20who%20like%20to%20watch%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHDR%3C%2Fa%3E%20(high%20dynamic%20range)%20movies%20and%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20software%20front%2C%20Samsung%20announced%20new%20%26quot%3BVision%20AI%26quot%3B%20features%20that%20leverage%20AI%20to%20enhance%20search%20and%20video%2Faudio%20optimizations.%20Vision%20AI%20includes%20the%20latest%20iterations%20of%20some%20picture%20and%20sound%20options%20that%20the%20company%20has%20already%20been%20offering%20for%20several%20years%20now%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20new%20features.%20Most%20notably%2C%20there's%20a%20function%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20learn%20about%20the%20performers%20and%20products%20i