ly-benin-attack%2Famp_articleshow%2F117128290.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fal-qaeda-linked-jihadist-group-claims-deadly-benin-attack%2Famp_articleshow%2F117128290.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Issues%20%2425-Million%20Bounty%20On%20Venezuela%20President%20On%20Day%20Of%20His%20Oath%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVenezuelan%20President%20Nicolas%20Maduro%2C%20whose%20nearly%2012%20years%20in%20office%20have%20been%20marked%20by%20deep%20economic%20and%20social%20crisis%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20for%20a%20third%20term%20on%20Friday%2C%20despite%20a%20six-month-long%20election%20dispute%2C%20international%20calls%20for%20him%20to%20stand%20aside%20and%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20US%20reward%20offered%20for%20his%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaduro%2C%20president%20since%202013%2C%20was%20declared%20the%20winner%20of%20July's%20election%20by%20both%20Venezuela's%20electoral%20authority%20and%20top%20court%2C%20though%20detailed%20tallies%20confirming%20his%20victory%20have%20never%20been%20published.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenezuela's%20opposition%20says%20ballot%20box-level%20tallies%20show%20a%20landslide%20win%20for%20its%20former%20candidate%20Edmundo%20Gonzalez%2C%20who%20is%20recognized%20as%20president-elect%20by%20several%20countries%20including%20the%20United%20States.%20International%20election%20observers%20said%20the%20vote%20was%20not%20democratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20months%20since%20the%20election%20have%20seen%20Gonzalez's%20flight%20to%20Spain%20in%20September%2C%20his%20ally%20Maria%20Corina%20Machado%20going%20into%20hiding%20in%20Venezuela%2C%20and%20the%20detentions%20of%20high-profile%20opposition%20figures%20and%20protesters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20series%20of%20punitive%20steps%2C%20the%20outgoing%20Biden%20administration%20increased%20its%20reward%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20the%20arrest%20or%20conviction%20of%20Maduro%20on%20drug%20trafficking%20charges%20to%20%2425%20million%2C%20from%20a%20previous%20%2415%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20issued%20a%20%2425%20million%20reward%20for%20Interior%20Minister%20Diosdado%20Cabello%20and%20a%20%2415%20million%20reward%20for%20Defense%20Minister%20Vladimir%20Padrino%2C%20as%20well%20as%20new%20sanctions%20against%20eight%20other%20officials%20including%20the%20head%20of%20state%20oil%20company%20PDVSA%20Hector%20Obregon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20indicted%20Maduro%20and%20others%20on%20narcotics%20and%20corruption%20charges%2C%20among%20others%2C%20in%202020.%20Maduro%20has%20rejected%20the%20accusations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20move%20coincided%20with%20sanctions%20by%20Britain%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20each%20targeting%2015%20officials%2C%20including%20members%20of%20the%20National%20Electoral%20Council%20and%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20and%20Canadian%20sanctions%20targeting%2014%20current%20and%20former%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maduro%20government%20has%20always%20rejected%20all%20sanctions%2C%20saying%20they%20are%20illegitimate%20measures%20that%20amount%20to%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20war%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20cripple%20Venezuela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20outgoing%20government%20of%20the%20United%20States%20doesn't%20know%20how%20to%20take%20revenge%20on%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Maduro%20said%20during%20his%20inauguration%20speech%2C%20without%20directly%20mentioning%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Venezuelan%20communications%20ministry%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaduro%20and%20his%20allies%20have%20cheered%20what%20they%20say%20is%20the%20country's%20resilience%20despite%20the%20measures%2C%20though%20they%20have%20historically%20blamed%20some%20economic%20hardships%20and%20shortages%20on%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOPPOSITION%20TO%20SPEAK%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGonzalez%2C%20who%20has%20been%20on%20a%20whistle-stop%20tour%20of%20the%20Americas%20this%20week%2C%20has%20said%20he%20will%20return%20to%20Venezuela%20to%20take%20up%20the%20mantle%20of%20president%2C%20but%20has%20given%20no%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20which%20has%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20fomenting%20fascist%20plots%20against%20it%2C%20has%20said%20Gonzalez%20will%20be%20arrested%20if%20he%20returns%20and%20offered%20a%20%24100%2C000%20reward%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20capture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20Gonzalez%20and%20Machado%20are%20each%20expected%20to%20speak%20later%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20are%20being%20investigated%20by%20the%20attorney%20general's%20office%20for%20alleged%20conspiracy%2C%20but%20only%20Gonzalez%20has%20a%20public%20warrant%20out%20for%20his%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMachado's%20first%20public%20appearance%20since%20August%20at%20an%20anti-government%20march%20in%20Caracas%20on%20Thursday%20was%20marred%20by%20a%20brief%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20Vente%20Venezuela%20political%20movement%20said%20guns%20were%20fired%20and%20Machado%20was%20knocked%20off%20the%20motorcycle%20on%20which%20she%20was%20leaving%20the%20event.%20She%20was%20then%20held%20and%20forced%20to%20film%20several%20videos%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20video%20shared%20on%20social%20media%20and%20by%20government%20officials%20showed%20her%20sitting%20on%20a%20curb%20and%20recounting%20losing%20her%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20scoffed%20at%20the%20incident%20and%20denied%20any%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%2042%20people%20have%20been%20detained%20for%20political%20reasons%20since%20Tuesday%2C%20judicial%20NGO%20Foro%20Penal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaduro%20was%20sworn%20in%20at%20the%20national%20assembly%20in%20Caracas%20and%20said%20he%20was%20taking%20his%20oath%20in%20the%20name%20of%20sixteenth-century%20Indigenous%20leader%20Guaicaipuro%20and%20late%20President%20Hugo%20Chavez%2C%20his%20mentor%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMay%20this%20new%20presidential%20term%20be%20a%20period%20of%20peace%2C%20of%20prosperity%2C%20of%20equality%20and%20the%20new%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Maduro%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20would%20convene%20a%20commission%20dedicated%20to%20constitutional%20reform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20act%20is%20possible%20because%20Venezuela%20is%20peaceful%2C%20in%20full%20exercise%20of%20its%20national%20sovereignty%2C%20of%20its%20popular%20sovereignty%2C%20of%20its%20national%20independence%2C%26quot%3B%20Maduro%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%202%2C000%20invitees%20from%20125%20countries%20attended%20the%20inauguration%2C%20according%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuba's%20President%20Miguel%20Diaz-Canel%20and%20Nicaragua's%20President%20Daniel%20Ortega%2C%20staunch%20allies%20of%20Maduro%2C%20attended%20as%20did%20Vyacheslav%20Volodin%2C%20the%20speaker%20of%20Russia's%20lower%20house%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EECONOMIC%20TROUBLES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenezuela%20closed%20its%20borders%20and%20airspace%20to%20Colombia%20for%2072%20hours%20starting%20at%200500%20local%20time%20(1000%20GMT)%2C%20the%20foreign%20ministry%20in%20Bogota%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20the%20border%20on%20the%20Colombian%20side%20would%20remain%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20non-governmental%20organizations%20and%20international%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20United%20Nations%20have%20for%20years%20decried%20increasing%20repression%20of%20opposition%20political%20parties%2C%20activists%20and%20independent%20media%20in%20Venezuela.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20said%20the%20country%20is%20being%20run%20by%20a%20dictator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20government%20has%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20opposition%20of%20plotting%20with%20foreig