0any%20jail%20time%20or%20penalty%20because%20he%20has%20been%20elected%20President%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20will%20take%20oath%20to%20the%20country's%20highest%20office%20on%20January%2020%20-%20a%20post%20that%20brings%20with%20itself%20an%20impunity%20of%20being%20above%20the%20law%20while%20in%20office%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20though%20the%2034%20counts%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20falsifying%20business%20records%20on%20which%20he%20was%20convicted%20in%20May%202024%20carried%20potential%20jail%20time%2C%20the%20judge%20could%20do%20little%20about%20it%2C%20ending%20up%20having%20to%20spare%20the%20President-elect.%20Should%20he%20not%20have%20been%20the%20president%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20would%20have%20been%20jailed%20for%20a%20term%20of%20four%20years.%20Instead%20he%20will%20now%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20as%20President%20for%20another%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-stormy-daniels-porn-star-at-center-of-donald-trumps-criminal-conviction-5783027%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWho%20Is%20Stormy%20Daniels%2C%20Porn%20Star%20At%20Center%20Of%20Trump's%20Criminal%20Conviction%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump%20did%20not%20even%20attend%20the%20session%20of%20court%20in%20person%2C%20choosing%20to%20do%20so%20virtually%2C%20knowing%20well%20that%20he%20would%20not%20be%20sent%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Stormy%20Daniels%20had%20testified%20in%20vivid%20detail%20about%20her%20alleged%20encounter%20with%20Trump%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Navada.%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Stormy%20Daniels%20had%20testified%20in%20vivid%20detail%20about%20her%20alleged%20encounter%20with%20Trump%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Navada.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fd29oiflk_stormy-daniels-reuters_625x300_10_January_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3EStormy%20Daniels%20had%20testified%20in%20vivid%20detail%20about%20her%20alleged%20encounter%20with%20Trump%20in%20a%20hotel%20in%20Navada.%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20court%20has%20determined%20that%20the%20only%20lawful%20sentence%20that%20permits%20entry%20of%20a%20judgement%20of%20conviction%20without%20encroaching%20on%20the%20highest%20office%20of%20the%20land%2C%20is%20an%20unconditional%20discharge%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20New%20York%20judge%20Juan%20Merchan%20delivering%20the%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20judge%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3BNever%20before%20has%20this%20court%20been%20presented%20with%20such%20a%20unique%20and%20remarkable%20set%20of%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%20With%20the%20constitution%20protecting%20the%20highest%20office%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20there%20was%20no%20other%20option%20for%20the%20judge%20than%20to%20give%20an%20%26quot%3Bunconditional%20discharge%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20former%20president.%20Any%20other%20judgement%20risked%20encroaching%20the%20Presidential%20immunity%20accorded%20to%20the%20country's%20highest%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20sentencing%2C%20to%20avoid%20the%20dubious%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20first%20felon%20ever%20in%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20used%20all%20his%20power%20and%20resources%20in%20making%20a%20last-ditch%20effort%20to%20skirt%20past%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20sentencing%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20remarked%20that%20he%20believes%20this%20entire%20legal%20proceeding%20was%20actually%20a%20%26quot%3Bsetback%20for%20the%20New%20York%20court%20system%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20done%20to%20damage%20my%20reputation%2C%20just%20so%20that%20I%20may%20lose%20the%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20has%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20experience%26quot%3B%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%