iscussions%20regarding%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission's%20(UGC)%20recent%20draft%20guidelines%2C%20which%20proposed%20making%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(NET)%20optional%20for%20faculty%20positions%2C%20UGC%20Chairman%20M%20Jagadesh%20Kumar%20has%20addressed%20the%20confusion%20surrounding%20the%20matter.%20In%20a%20video%20shared%20on%20the%20microblogging%20site%20X%2C%20the%20Chairman%20clarified%20that%20the%20interpretation%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%2C%20suggesting%20that%20UGC%20NET%20is%20no%20longer%20required%2C%20was%20inaccurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20confusion%20stemmed%20from%20claims%20suggesting%20that%20candidates%20with%20only%20a%20master's%20degree%20could%20now%20apply%20directly%20for%20faculty%20roles%20without%20the%20UGC-NET%20qualification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%9E%A1%EF%B8%8F%20As%20per%202025%20draft%20regulations%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20PG%20degree%20(NCrF%20Level%206.5)%20with%20at%20least%2055%25%20marks%20(or%20an%20equivalent%20grade)%20in%20disciplines%20such%20as%20Arts%2C%20Commerce%2C%20Humanities%2C%20Education%2C%20Law%2C%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Sciences%2C%20Languages%2C%20Library%20Science%2C%20Physical%20Education%2C%20Journalism%20%26amp%3B%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTdxAWRLYZq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTdxAWRLYZq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20UGC%20INDIA%20(%40ugc_india)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fugc_india%2Fstatus%2F1877680839288578173%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%2010%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UGC%20chief%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20talks%20on%20social%20media%20that%2C%20from%20now%20onwards%2C%20there%20is%20no%20need%20for%20UGC-NET.%20If%20someone%20has%20a%20master's%20degree%2C%20they%20can%20directly%20apply%20for%20faculty%20positions%20in%20higher%20educational%20institutions.%20That%20is%20wrong.%20The%20UGC-NET%20is%20still%20required%20if%20you%20have%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20non-professional%20programmes.%20However%2C%20for%20professional%20programmes%2C%20such%20as%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20ME%20or%20MTech%2C%20you%20don't%20need%20the%20UGC-NET%20qualification%20for%20appointment%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor.%20This%20is%20in%20line%20with%20the%20AICTE%20recruitment%20rules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20candidates%20holding%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20non-professional%20programs%2C%20such%20as%20Arts%2C%20Humanities%2C%20or%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20the%20UGC-NET%20remains%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20for%20appointment%20as%20an%20assistant%20professor.%20However%2C%20candidates%20with%20a%20master's%20degree%20in%20professional%20programmes%20like%20Engineering%20or%20Technology%20(e.g.%2C%20ME%20or%20MTech)%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20NET%20requirement.%20This%20aligns%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Council%20for%20Technical%20Education%20(AICTE)%20recruitment%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20draft%20guidelines%2C%20set%20for%202025%2C%20outline%20the%20qualification%20criteria%20for%20faculty%20positions%20across%20various%20disciplines.%20To%20be%20eligible%20for%20an%20assistant%20professor%20role%20in%20subjects%20such%20as%20Arts%2C%20Commerce%2C%20Humanities%2C%20Law%2C%20Social%20Sciences%2C%20Sciences%2C%20Languages%2C%20Journalism%2C%20Management%2C%20and%20more%2C%20candidates%20must%20hold%20a%20postgraduate%20degree%20with%20at%20least%2055%25%20marks%20(or%20an%20equivalent%20grade)%20and%20pass%20the%20National%20Eligibility%20Test%20(NET)%2C%20SET%2C%20or%20SLET.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20field%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Technology%2C%20candidates%20with%20a%20postgraduate%20degree%20(e.g.%2C%20ME%20or%20MTech)%20with%20at%20least%2055%25%20marks%20are%20eligible%20for%20appointment%20without%20the%20need%20for%20the%20NET%20qualification%2C%20per%20AICTE%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20candidates%20with%20a%20PhD%20in%20any%20discipline%20are%20exempt%20from%20the%20NET%20requirement%20and%20can%20be%20appointed%20as%20assistant%20professors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20fields%20like%20Drama%2C%20Yoga%2C%20Music%2C%20Performing%20Arts%2C%20Visual%20Arts%2C%20and%20Traditional%20Indian%20Art%20Forms%20such%20as%20Sculpture%2C%20applicants%20with%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%20and%20professional%20attainments%20are%20also%20eligible%20for%20assistant%20professor%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736522100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F59t80glg_ugc-chairman-m-jagadesh-kumar_625x300_10_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnet-not-required-for-faculty-positions-heres-what-ugc-chief-has-to-say-7444628%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20confusion%20stemmed%20from%20claims%20suggesting%20that%20candidates%20with%20only%20a%20master's%20degree%20could%20now%20directly%20apply%20for%20faculty%20roles%20without%20the%20UGC-NET%20qualification.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnet-not-required-for-faculty-positions-heres-what-ugc-chief-has-to-say-7444628%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20to%20impose%20sanctions%20on%20Russian%20oil%2C%20Indian%20supplies%20may%20be%20hit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736522079000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fnew-us-sanctions-on-russian-tankers-to-disrupt-india-s-oil-supplies-125011000954_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20sources%20said%20they%20understand%20that%20the%20new%20US%20sanctions%20would%20target%20more%20than%20180%20tankers%20shipping%20Russian%20oil%20and%20Rus