icised%20for%20his%20alleged%20interference%20in%20Europe's%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Meloni%20said%20Elon%20Musk's%20comments%20about%20politics%20in%20Europe%20on%20his%20social%20media%20platform%20X%20does%20not%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20in%20any%20way.%20She%20compared%20him%20to%20billionaire%20George%20Soros%2C%20saying%20the%20latter%20is%20what%20a%20threat%20to%20democracy%20and%20political%20interference%20really%20looks%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20foreigners%20have%20for%20long%20been%20interfering%20in%20Europe's%20politics%2C%20the%20Italian%20prime%20minister%20questioned%20reporters%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20is%20only%20exercising%20his%20right%20to%20free%20speech%26quot%3B.%20She%20wondered%20if%20the%20problem%20was%20that%20he%20happens%20to%20be%20rich%20and%20has%20views%20that%20are%20'right%20of%20centre'.%20%26quot%3BIs%20the%20problem%20(with%20Elon%20Musk)%20that%20he%20is%20rich%20and%20influential%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20because%20he%20is%20not%20left-wing%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20example%20of%20George%20Soros%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20it%20is%20well-known%20how%20rich%20and%20powerful%20people%20with%20%26quot%3Bleft-wing%20ideologies%26quot%3B%20have%20indulged%20in%20political%20interference%20of%20other%20democracies%2C%20concluding%20that%20%26quot%3BMusk%20does%20not%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20democracies%2C%20George%20Soros%20does.%2C%26quot%3B%20to%20which%20Elon%20Musk%20quickly%20responded%20on%20X%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BAnd%20Soros%20is%20being%20defeated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Meloni%20further%20said%20that%20she%20had%20not%20taken%20any%20money%20from%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20%26quot%3Bunlike%20those%20who%20have%20taken%20it%20from%20Soros%26quot%3B.%20She%20also%20denied%20media%20reports%20that%20her%20government%20in%20Italy%20is%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20signing%20a%20giant%2C%20and%20controversial%2C%20cybersecurity%20deal%20with%20Elon%20Musk's%20company%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20whose%20massive%20support%20to%20Donald%20Trump%20helped%20him%20win%20the%20US%20election%2C%20is%20now%20facing%20severe%20criticism%20by%20liberals%20across%20Europe%20for%20his%20string%20of%20attacks%20on%20several%20European%20leaders%20on%20his%20social%20media%20website%20X.%20In%20particular%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20has%20strongly%20targeted%20UK%20prime%20minister%20Kier%20Starmer%20and%20German%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20worried%20many%20in%20Europe%2C%20which%20is%20already%20seeing%20a%20surge%20in%20support%20for%20the%20right%20or%20far-right%20across%20the%20continent.%20Addressing%20those%20concerns%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Ms%20Meloni%20said%20Elon%20Musk's%20views%20on%20X%20can%20in%20no%20way%20be%20termed%20as%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%20interference%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20a%20problem%20when%20wealthy%20people%20use%20their%20resources%20to%20finance%20certain%20political%20parties%2C%20associations%2C%20organisations%20and%20political%20exponents%20all%20over%20the%20world%20to%20influence%20the%20political%20choices%20of%20nation%20states%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Meloni%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BThat's%20not%20what%20Musk%20is%20doing%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20financing%20political%20parties%2C%20associations%20or%20political%20exponents%20around%20the%20world.%20This%2C%20for%20example%2C%20is%20what%20George%20Soros%20does%20-%20And%20yes%2C%20I%20consider%20that%20to%20be%20dangerous%20interference%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20nation%20states%20and%20in%20their%20sovereignty%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Soros%20has%20used%20the%20wealth%20he%20has%20amassed%20as%20a%20financier%20in%20the%201970s%20and%2080s%20to%20create%20the%20Open%20Society%20Foundations%20or%20OSF%2C%20which%20supports%20and%20funds%20a%20broad%20network%20of%20%26quot%3Bcauses%26quot%3B%20and%20NGOs%20worldwide%2C%20rang.%20His%20foundation%20reportedly%20claims%20that%20this%20is%20done%20to%20promote%20good-governance%2C%20liberal%20public%20policy%20initiatives%2C%20and%20democracy-building%20programmes.%20Though%20Soros%20and%20his%20foundation%20face%20serious%20charges%20of%20political%20interference%2C%20promoting%20social%20anarchy%2C%20funding%20political%20parties%20during%20elections%2C%20among%20others.%20He%20is%20often%20also%20targeted%20for%20anti-Semitic%20conspiracies.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736513700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Facg9g9vs_italian-pm-giorgia-meloni-ians_625x300_30_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgeorge-soros-indulges-in-political-interference-italys-giorgia-meloni-7443886%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22George%20Soros%20interferes%20in%20the%20domestic%20politics%20of%20other%20nations%20and%20uses%20his%20money%20to%20destabilise%20countries%2C%20Italian%20prime%20minister%20Giorgia%20Meloni%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fgeorge-soros-indulges-in-political-interference-italys-giorgia-meloni-7443886%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20Trudeau%20Really%20Make%20A%20Counter-Offer%20For%20%26quot%3BParts%26quot%3B%20Of%20Canada%20With%20Trump%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20revealed%20that%20he%20jokingly%20suggested%20trading%20Vermont%20or%20California%20to%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20interest%20in%20annexing%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20shared%20this%20exchange%20during%20an%20MSNBC%20interview%2C%20recalling%20his%20visit%20with%20Trump%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20in%20November.%20Trudeau%20sa