the%20US%20and%20Canada.%20Trudeau%2C%20however%2C%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20Trump's%20tariff%20plan%2C%20stating%20that%20Canada%20is%20prepared%20to%20deliver%20a%20%26quot%3Brobust%20response%26quot%3B%20if%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20told%20MSNBC's%20Jen%20Psaki%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20focus%20has%20to%20be%20not%20on%20something%20that%20he's%20talking%20about%20that%20will%20not%20ever%20happen%20but%20more%20on%20something%20that%20might%20well%20happen...%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20have%20a%20robust%20response%20to%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20proposed%20imposing%20blanket%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%2C%20citing%20the%20ongoing%20fentanyl%20crisis.%20This%20plan%20would%20be%20among%20his%20first%20executive%20orders%20in%20his%20second%20term.%20In%20response%2C%20Trudeau%20announced%20his%20resignation%20as%20the%20head%20of%20Canada's%20ruling%20Liberal%20Party%2C%20partly%20due%20to%20criticism%20over%20his%20handling%20of%20Trump's%20threats.%20Deputy%20Prime%20Minister%20Chrystia%20Freeland%20had%20previously%20resigned%2C%20expressing%20concerns%20over%20Trudeau's%20approach%20to%20the%20incoming%20tariff%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Trudeau%20has%20said%20Trump's%20talk%20of%20annexing%20Canada%20is%20just%20a%20tactic%20that%20he%20is%20deploying%20to%20distract%20people%20from%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20proposed%20tariffs.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20think%20is%20happening%20in%20this%20is%20President%20Trump%2C%20who%20is%20a%20very%20skilful%20negotiator%2C%20is%20getting%20people%20to%20be%20somewhat%20distracted%20by%20that%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20Trudeau%20told%20CNN.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736513040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F3to61go8_donald-trump-justin-trudeau_625x300_10_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-justin-trudeau-really-make-a-counter-offer-for-parts-of-canada-with-donald-trump-7443875%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20revealed%20that%20he%20jokingly%20suggested%20trading%20Vermont%20or%20California%20to%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20response%20to%20Trump's%20interest%20in%20annexing%20Canada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdid-justin-trudeau-really-make-a-counter-offer-for-parts-of-canada-with-donald-trump-7443875%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20The%20Congress%20Is%20Fast%20Losing%20Friends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBarely%20six%20months%20after%20its%20forceful%20rise%20on%20the%20national%20political%20horizon%2C%20the%20Indian%20National%20Development%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20formed%20by%20diverse%20parties%20united%20by%20the%20sole%20ideological%20adhesive%E2%80%94an%20anti-Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20sentiment%E2%80%94is%20now%20tottering%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20disintegration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20where%20the%20alliance%20fell%2060%20seats%20short%20of%20the%20strength%20acquired%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20provided%20a%20significant%20boost%20to%20the%20combined%20opposition.%20The%20alliance's%20strength%20was%20enough%20to%20counter%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government's%20proclivity%20to%20pass%20laws%20unchallenged.%20A%20collective%20opposition%20of%20around%2020%20parties%20led%20to%20crucial%20bills%E2%80%94such%20as%20those%20on%20Waqf%20properties%20and%20One%20Nation%20One%20Election%E2%80%94being%20referred%20to%20parliamentary%20panels%20for%20detailed%20scrutiny.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHowever%2C%20by%202025%2C%20distinct%20grumbling%20voices%20from%20within%20the%20alliance%20suggested%20that%20it%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20drift%2C%20lacking%20demonstrable%20leadership%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20failing%20to%20provide%20coordination.%20This%20discontent%20became%20more%20pronounced%20when%20a%20few%20constituents%20endorsed%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20which%20is%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%20on%20February%205.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Implosive%20System%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drifting%20state%20of%20the%20alliance%2C%20the%20Congress's%20unwillingness%20to%20accommodate%20its%20partners%20in%20the%20Haryana%20assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20its%20current%20stance%20as%20a%20challenger%20to%20AAP%20in%20Delhi%2C%20highlight%20the%20inherent%20contradictions%20within%20this%20arrangement.%20Over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20the%20AAP%20has%20captured%20the%20imagination%20of%20Delhi's%20residents%2C%20filling%20the%20political%20space%20that%20was%20once%20dominated%20by%20Congress.%20The%20AAP%20is%20now%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20equalling%20the%20Congress's%20record%20of%20forming%20a%20government%20in%20Delhi%20for%20three%20consecutive%20terms.%20The%2015-year%20run%20of%20the%20Congress%20between%201998%20and%202013%20was%20halted%20by%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20AAP%2C%20formed%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20fellow%20travellers%20on%20an%20%E2%80%9Canti-corruption%E2%80%9D%20bandwagon.%20The%20Congress%2C%20now%20desperate%20to%20regain%20some%20of%20the%20ground%20it%20lost%2C%20is%20back%20in%20the%20fray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20convenor%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20party%20has%20secured%20support%20from%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20Congress%20and%20endorsement%20from%20other%20INDIA%20allies.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20hoping%20to%20form%20a%20government%20in%20Delhi%20after%2026%20years%2C%20is%20playing%20up%20these%20differences%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EParliament%20vs.%20Assemblies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20clear%20strands%20have%20emerged%20over%20the%20past%20six%20months.%20The%20combined%20alliance%20in%20Parliament%20is%20different%20from%20its%20ability%20to%20accommodate%20constituents%20in%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20As%20the%20largest%20party%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20other%20constituents%20expect%20the%20Congress%20to%20be%20magnanimous%2C%20without%20expecting%20reciprocity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%209%2C%20Kejriwal%20was%20emphatic%20in%20declaring%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20non-existent%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20the%20contest%20is%20primarily%20between%20the%20AAP%20and%20the%20BJP.%20His%20comments%20echoed%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20who%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20alliance%20was%20meant%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20This%20is%20part%20of%20the%20RJD's%20posturing%20ahead%20of%20the%20Bihar%20assembly%20polls%20due%20this%20autumn.%20In%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20went%20a%20step%20further%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20alliance%20should%20either%20define%20clear%20contours%20of%20engagement%20in%20states%20or%20disband%20entirely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20under%20attack%20as%20allies%20mount%20pressure%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20mantle%20of%20leadership%20to%20another%20player%2C%20unwilling%20as%20they%20are%20to%20be%20led%20by%20the%20Grand%20Old%20Party.%20The%20voices%20grew%20louder%20after%20the%20Congress%20failed%20to%20regain%20power%20in%20Haryana%20in%20October%2C%20which%20cost%20it%20a%20significant%20bargaining%20chip%20in%20the%20subsequent%20Maharashtra%20polls.%20This%20setback%20further%20eroded%20the%20Congress's%20ability%20to%20provide%20leadership%20to%20the%20alliance.%20Signs%20of%20unease%20were%20evident%20during%20the%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20natural%20for%20a%20party%20with%20a%20strong%20political%20base%20in%20a%20state%20to%20be%20unwilling%20to%20accommodate%20a%20weaker%20partner.%20During%20seat-sharing%20and%20adjustment%20talks%2C%20the%20strength%20that%20any%20party%20brings%20to%20the%20table%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Needs%20To%20Present%20A%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParties%20like%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20the%20AAP%2C%20with%20strong%20presences%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Bihar%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Punjab%2C%20respectively%2C%20will%20be%20reluctant%20to%20grant%20any%20space%20to%20an%20ally%20with%20a%20similar%20voter%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20the%20only%20party%20with%20a%20pan-India%20organisational%20presence%20capable%20of%20challenging%20the%20BJP%20across%20the%20country%2C%20must%20take%20charge.%20It%20needs%20to%20present%20a%20clear%20plan%20to%20coalition%20partners%2C%20adopting%20a%20discerning%20strategy%20for%20Parliament%20while%20maintaining%20flexibility%20in%20state%20politics%20and%20managing%20inherent%20contradictions.%20As%20the%20Congress%20prepares%20to%20move%20into%20its%20new%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%20on%20January%2015%2C%20it%20must%20shed%20its%20baggage%20and%20work%20toward%20a%20smooth%20transition%20with%20renewed%20enthusiasm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1736512980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvu8dmsjo_arvind-kejriwal-rahul-gandhi-rahul-kejriwal-650_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fcongress-is-fast-losing-the-support-of-allies-7443277%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20is%20under%20attack%20as%20allies%20mount%20pressure%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20mantle%20of%20leadership%20to%20another%20player%2C%20unwilling%20a