nes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%20%E2%80%9CDr%20Raghavan%20provided%20a%20monthly%20amount%20of%20Rs%20800%2C%20which%20was%20essential%20for%20my%20survival.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Raghavan%20also%20encouraged%20her%20to%20join%20the%20Community%20Action%20Network%20as%20an%20outreach%20worker.%20Despite%20her%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20raise%20awareness%20about%20HIV%2C%20Noori%20faced%20severe%20isolation%20and%20discrimination.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20pig%E2%80%99s%20fodder%20to%20eat%20as%20lunch%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls%20a%20disheartening%20experience%20during%20an%20outreach%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELiving%20with%20HIV%20often%20brings%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hurdles.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20stigma%20surrounding%20both%20my%20transgender%20identity%20and%20HIV%20status%20led%20many%20to%20fear%20and%20ostracise%20me%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%2C%20who%20were%20also%20living%20with%20the%20virus.%20I%20hated%20it%20when%20doctors%2C%20who%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20disease%2C%20ill-treat%20their%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20says.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20treated%20us%20like%20dogs%2C%20throwing%20stones%20at%20us%2C%20thinking%20that%20it%20is%20transmitted%20like%20the%20flu%20virus.%20I%20wanted%20to%20change%20that%20perspective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Noori%20continued%20undeterred%2C%20raising%20awareness%20about%20HIV%20and%20advocating%20for%20the%20compassionate%20treatment%20of%20all%20individuals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FMervin-Feature-image-5-1734611396-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-390996%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20holds%20over%2022%20leadership%20positions%20and%20possesses%20strong%20oratory%20and%20logical%20skills.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outreach%20worker%2C%20Noori%20started%20conducting%20meetings%20for%20people%20affected%20by%20HIV.%20It%20was%20during%20one%20of%20these%20meetings%20that%20she%20met%20Dr%20Joseph%20Williams%2C%20the%20then-director%20of%20VHS%20Hospital.%20Together%2C%20they%20established%20the%20South%20India%20Positive%20Network%2C%20an%20NGO%20for%20which%20Noori%20was%20elected%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDr%20Williams%20was%20instrumental%20in%20this%20endeavour%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20only%20did%20he%20guide%20us%20through%20the%20registration%20process%20but%20also%20provided%20crucial%20support%20in%20setting%20up%20the%20organisation.%20I%20consider%20him%20a%20trusted%20mentor%20even%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202001%2C%20for%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20AIDS%20Control%20Society%2C%20Noori%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20aid%20HIV%20positive%20individuals%2C%20written%20under%20the%20guidance%20of%20Dr%20Williams.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20secure%20the%20project%20to%20provide%20support%20and%20care%2C%20worth%20Rs%203.12%20lakh%20for%20their%20upliftment%2C%20and%20she%20executed%20the%20same%20skillfully%20with%20just%20three%20staff%20members.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20on%20over%2010%20projects%20and%20I%20was%20promoted%20to%20a%20position%20where%20I%20could%20recruit%20more%20than%2070%20staff.%20I%20have%20good%20oratory%20skills%20which%20have%20created%20an%20impact%20among%20the%20listeners%2C%20despite%20my%20poor%20educational%20background.%20This%20helped%20in%20my%20journey%20of%20leadership%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20beams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20shelter%20for%20the%20abandoned%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Noori%2C%20supported%20by%20Dr%20Williams%2C%20established%20the%20SIP%20Memorial%20Trust.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20me%20that%20I%20have%20good%20logical%20reasoning%20skills%2C%20so%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20hesitant%20thinking%20about%20her%20lack%20of%20education%20to%20lead%20a%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Noori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20other%20medical%20officials%20perceived%20my%20identity%20as%20just%20a%20transwoman%20who%20is%20HIV%20positive%2C%20Dr%20Joseph%20saw%20my%20potential%20and%20motivated%20me%20to%20start%20the%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20I%20named%20the%20trust%20SIP%20in%20memory%20of%20my%20three%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20Selvi%2C%20Indira%2C%20and%20Pazhani%20%E2%80%94%20who%20tragically%20lost%20their%20lives%20to%20HIV%2C%E2%80%9D%20Noori%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20Trust%20aimed%20to%20create%20awareness%20and%20outreach%20for%20HIV%20positive%20individuals.%20Later%2C%20Noori%20started%20focusing%20on%20rescuing%20infants%20and%20children%20who%20were%20abandoned%20because%20of%20HIV.%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20experienced%20a%20challenging%20childhood%20myself%2C%20I%20deeply%20understand%20the%20lasting%20impact%20that%20parents%20and%20caregivers%20have%20on%20a%20child%E2%80%99s%20mindset.%20These%20children%20are%20not%20to%20blame%20for%20their%20HIV%20status%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Noori%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20for%20these%20children%2C%20saving%20nothing%20for%20herself.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-300x226.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-500x376.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FThumbnail_v1kdhj_1563274483_11zon-1734611645-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-391006%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENoori%20has%20dedicated%20her%20life%20for%20these%20children%2C%20saving%E2%80%9DI%20haven%E2%80%99t%20saved%20anything%20for%20myself.%20Al