eing%20respected.%20We%20had%20nothing%20to%20our%20name%20%E2%80%94%20no%20land%2C%20no%20work%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20that%20respect.%20My%20only%20goal%20was%20to%20do%20something%20that%20would%20earn%20my%20family%20and%20me%20that%20honour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20would%20never%20be%20a%20landowner%2C%20nor%20would%20I%20become%20extremely%20wealthy%2C%20but%20I%20promised%20myself%20I%20would%20work%20tirelessly%20to%20earn%20that%20respect.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20shaped%20me%20into%20the%20person%20I%20am%20today%20%E2%80%94%20my%20character%2C%20my%20work%2C%20and%20my%20commitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%201980s%2C%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20rising%20in-state%20tensions%2C%20the%20people%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%2C%20including%20Sarbeswar%E2%80%99s%20village%2C%20began%20claiming%20forest%20land%20as%20their%20own.%20With%20no%20other%20place%20to%20farm%2C%20they%20took%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands%2C%20turning%20the%20jungle%20into%20usable%20land%20for%20cultivation.%20Sarbeswar%2C%20too%2C%20became%20involved%20in%20clearing%20and%20preparing%20the%20land%20for%20farming.%20He%20leased%20a%2012-acre%20plot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20a%20strong%20willingness%20to%20learn%2C%20Sarbeswar%20began%20farming%20with%20traditional%20methods.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20what%20I%20saw%20other%20elders%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20growing%20eggplant%2C%20chilli%2C%20Assam%20lemon%2C%20and%20other%20vegetables%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarbeswar%20recalls.%20However%2C%20the%20methods%20proved%20insufficient%2C%20and%20the%20land%20lacked%20the%20fertili